  <!--
    Reviewed suppressions (Chapter 16: suppress with a reason, never disable a whole detector).

    This module has NONE. The production code is a stateless discount calculator over an immutable
    Money record plus an AtomicLong counter, so SpotBugs's representation-exposure and mutability
    detectors stay quiet without any suppression. The filter is kept (empty) so a future,
    genuinely-reviewed false positive has a home with a reason, rather than being added inline or
    silenced by switching a detector off.
  -->
